      "id": "81b896bc2e4c1baf",
      "text": "Managing complexity through managing [[scale]] is a big deal and generally not well considered. See [[geopolitical scale]]. Maybe we can talk of [[Geopolitical Rhythms]] and scale can add a musical meaning."
